features: 【𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐯𝐞𝐧𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐠𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐇𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐛𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝】Equipped with 2 Outlets & 2 USB Ports and a 5.9 ft cord, our king bed frame with storage offers hassle-free device charging while in bed. Its sleek design adds a modern touch to your bedroom, perfect for charging phones or reading with a lamp. The storage shelf adds practicality and style to your home.

【𝐈𝐧𝐝𝐮𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐑𝐞𝐭𝐫𝐨 𝐒𝐭𝐲𝐥𝐞】Combining vintage aesthetics with a black upholstered king bed frame featuring charging ports, our bed effortlessly complements any room. The blend of retro wooden headboard & footboard with black metal creates a unique charm. The black and retro brown combination adds timeless elegance.
【𝐀𝐦𝐩𝐥𝐞 𝐔𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐫-𝐁𝐞𝐝 𝐒𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐚𝐠𝐞】With 10.6 inches of clearance, our bed provides space for odds and ends. It easily accommodates boxes, shoes, etc., conveniently maintained by a sweeping robot.

【𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐝𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧】Enhanced by heavy-duty metal slats, our bed ensures stability, eliminating noise and squeaks during nighttime. It supports all mattress types without a box spring, offering comfortable back support while sitting up. The platform bed combines P2 high-quality MDF board wood grain with a black PU leather king bed frame with storage and outlets and footboard, seamlessly complementing your furniture.

【𝐄𝐟𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐥𝐲】Assembly of the king-size bed frame takes around an hour. Labeled parts and clear instructions simplify the process. The snap-fit design enables two individuals to assemble the platform bed within 30 minutes. Follow step-by-step instructions for a seamless experience.
